    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Wilderness pg. 243</em><br/><strong>Price</strong> 4 gp; <strong>Weight</strong> -<br/><strong>Category</strong> Clothing</p><h2 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"https://www.aonprd.com/images/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\" title=\"PFS Legal\"/>Description</h2><p>This is an extra pocket sewn on the inside of a piece of clothing. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus on Sleight of Hand checks to conceal an item in an inside pocket. Detecting the compartment requires a successful DC 15 Perception check at minimum (DC 20 if empty), even if you aren't trained in Sleight of Hand.<br/><br/> The inside pocket is 1 inch deep. Different styles open from the top or from the side, and some have button flaps to secure the contents.</p>",
